01:22:32.127 --> 01:22:34.701
She writes text for Atmos.

01:22:35.430 --> 01:22:38.005
- You said her name was Nia?
- Yes.

01:22:40.401 --> 01:22:42.570
Was she brought here yesterday evening?

01:22:42.670 --> 01:22:45.745
- Lives at 6L 415?
- That's right.

01:22:46.674 --> 01:22:49.015
She died last night.

01:22:49.477 --> 01:22:53.186
According to the doctor's notes,
the cause of death was asphyxiation.

01:22:55.450 --> 01:22:58.558
Could you... could you check that again?

01:23:03.057 --> 01:23:05.098
Yes, that's her.

01:23:14.302 --> 01:23:16.143
Sir?

01:23:17.405 --> 01:23:19.679
Are you okay?

01:23:21.843 --> 01:23:24.384
Do you need some help?

01:26:49.984 --> 01:26:52.358
Where have you been?

01:26:53.354 --> 01:26:55.229
Hey.

01:27:02.163 --> 01:27:04.434
You okay?

01:27:13.491 --> 01:27:15.265
Why?

01:27:17.478 --> 01:27:20.453
I thought... I thought you were gone.

01:27:28.890 --> 01:27:31.719
How long do you have?

01:27:31.859 --> 01:27:34.334
Maybe five hours.

01:27:44.973 --> 01:27:46.813
Silas.

01:27:52.113 --> 01:27:53.920
Hey.

01:27:56.250 --> 01:27:58.524
Fight it.

01:28:00.154 --> 01:28:04.159
It doesn't matter, it doesn't matter.
Fight it. Okay?

01:28:04.859 --> 01:28:07.066
I'm still pregnant.

01:28:13.701 --> 01:28:17.370
We're going to get
on the train tomorrow. Okay?

01:28:21.309 --> 01:28:23.550
I love you.

01:28:25.279 --> 01:28:29.756
I love you, I love you, I love you,
I love you, I love you.

01:28:43.865 --> 01:28:47.068
You have to fight it. Just fight it, okay?

01:28:47.668 --> 01:28:50.376
I can already tell it's in me.

01:28:53.441 --> 01:28:56.978
Just remember... okay?

01:28:57.578 --> 01:28:59.452
How?

01:29:03.317 --> 01:29:05.658
Remember this feeling.

01:29:07.989 --> 01:29:10.863
Just remember what this feels like.

01:29:12.360 --> 01:29:16.478
Yeah, just promise me, no matter...

01:29:16.578 --> 01:29:20.135
what happens you keep loving me,
no matter what I say,

01:29:20.235 --> 01:29:25.040
what I feel or don't feel, I'm still...
I'm still in here trying. Okay?

01:29:25.140 --> 01:29:29.044
I'm still in here.
Just don't give up on me.

01:29:29.144 --> 01:29:32.732
- Please, don't give up on me.
- I promise.

01:29:33.361 --> 01:29:36.141
I promise that I won't...

01:30:25.866 --> 01:30:27.574
Silas?

01:30:31.739 --> 01:30:33.913
Good morning.

01:30:41.482 --> 01:30:43.723
Do you still love me?

01:30:50.124 --> 01:30:52.694
I remember I loved you.

01:30:53.394 --> 01:30:55.235
But...

01:30:57.098 --> 01:30:59.472
I don't feel it anymore.

01:31:05.973 --> 01:31:08.347
Do you still want to go?

01:31:09.777 --> 01:31:12.084
We made a plan.

01:31:19.020 --> 01:31:20.894
Right.

